<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhǔ qiú nǐ gěi wǒ yī kē dǎo gào de xīn 迦南372</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ qiú nǐ gěi wǒ yī kē qí dǎo de xīn, gěi wǒ yī kē qí dǎo de xīn,
 jiào zhù yán jiē qǐ tǎo de rén, kuài huí lái ba,
 zhǔ qiú nǐ gěi wǒ yī shuāng qí dǎo de shǒu, gěi wǒ yī shuāng qí dǎo de shǒu,
 zài hēi yè lǐ, zài hēi yè lǐ, zhèn dòng de yù de mén.
 wǒ men yào dǎo gào fēng yǔ yě bù dòng yáo, wǒ men shì dǎo gào dà jūn,
 wǒ men yào dǎo gào, shén jiù zuò dà shì, wàn mín dōu pī shàng jiù ēn.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>372</hymn_number>
</song>